User Privacy and Data Policy for Background Remover SaaS

Effective Date: December 5, 2025

1. Introduction
This policy outlines how we collect, store, use, and protect user data in our background removal service. We are committed to transparency and minimal data collection.

2. Data Collection and Usage
- We collect no personal information such as names, emails, or addresses.
- Users are identified anonymously via unique session identifiers.
- Data collected includes:
  - Usage statistics for rate limiting and service management.
  - Batch processing records (number of images, processing type, payment status).
  - Temporary session data for workflow management.
  - Uploaded and processed image files.

3. Storage Types and Locations
- Database: Permanent storage for usage tracking and batch records.
- Session Storage: Temporary data during image processing workflows.
- File Storage: Uploaded and processed images stored securely and temporarily.
- Cache System: Session data stored temporarily for active sessions.

4. Data Retention
- Usage statistics and records: Retained permanently for service functionality.
- Processed images: Available for download for 2 hours, then automatically deleted.
- Temporary files: Cleaned up after payment processing (typically 2 hours).
- Session data: Expires after 24 hours of inactivity.

5. Data Security
- All data is encrypted in transit (HTTPS) and at rest where applicable.
- Payment processing is handled by secure third-party providers.
- Images are processed server-side and not shared with external parties.
- No data is sold, shared, or used for purposes beyond service delivery.
- Images are not viewed, accessed, or used by humans; all processing is fully automated.

6. User Rights
- Users can request data deletion by contacting support (though anonymous sessions limit this).
- Processed images are available for download within the 2-hour window.
- Users control uploads and can avoid using the service to minimize data.

7. Changes to Policy
We may update this policy; changes will be posted here.

8. Contact
For questions, email digitalbaku994@gmail.com
